		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="22.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Create Vision Statements">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Workshop participants create a vision statement for each action area that will be used to guide brainstorming actions.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Involving community participants in creating vision statements for the Action Areas identified will help ensure that the vision is broadly shared and begin the process of thinking about how the vision can be achieved.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Introduce the Action Areas and explain how they were selected">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Workshop participants break up into small groups, with at least one group for each action area">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Break-out groups create a vision statement for their Action Area, discussing who will &quot;What do we want this issue to look like in 10 years?&quot;">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	After the workshop, record the results in Key Takeaways Form on Strategizing Actions">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Italic"
			text="Example">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Action Area: Flooding is severely impacting residents of Parkview neighborhood.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Vision statement: In 10 years, the impacts of flooding should be reduced in Parkview neighborhood and residents should be better able to prepare for and recover from flooding.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Output">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
